Sentencas: Herein, we report a facilely synthesized Sm0.5Sr0.5CoO3 (SSC) nano-catalyst as a cathode material for the solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC).
Titulo: Facile and low-temperature synthesis approach to fabricate Sm0.5Sr0.5CoO3-δ cathode material for solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The SSC nano-catalyst was synthesized by a sol-gel process using citric acid and metal nitrates and calcination was performed at a relatively low temperature of 1250 celcius.
Titulo: Facile and low-temperature synthesis approach to fabricate Sm0.5Sr0.5CoO3-δ cathode material for solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The crystallinity and morphology of the catalyst were observed by the X-ray diffraction and scanning electron microscope.
Titulo: Facile and low-temperature synthesis approach to fabricate Sm0.5Sr0.5CoO3-δ cathode material for solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The average particle size of the SSC powder was 100 nm after calcination at 1250 degrees C.
Titulo: Facile and low-temperature synthesis approach to fabricate Sm0.5Sr0.5CoO3-δ cathode material for solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The resulting SSC material was employed as a cathode for the SOFC.
Titulo: Facile and low-temperature synthesis approach to fabricate Sm0.5Sr0.5CoO3-δ cathode material for solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The SOFC cell with highly active SSC showed a peak power density of 900 mWcm(-2) at 700 degrees C.
Titulo: Facile and low-temperature synthesis approach to fabricate Sm0.5Sr0.5CoO3-δ cathode material for solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The single cell with an SSC cathode showed excellent stability under the accelerated operating conditions of 0.5A/cm(2) and 650 degrees C for 1250 min.
Titulo: Facile and low-temperature synthesis approach to fabricate Sm0.5Sr0.5CoO3-δ cathode material for solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The cell performance was enhanced during the initial hours of the long-term operation which is attributed to the cathode activation process and improved cathode/buffer layer interface contact.
Titulo: Facile and low-temperature synthesis approach to fabricate Sm0.5Sr0.5CoO3-δ cathode material for solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: This work features a cost-effective, scalable, and reproducible method for the production of highly robust SSC cathode material for the SOFC under relatively low calcination temperatures.
Titulo: Facile and low-temperature synthesis approach to fabricate Sm0.5Sr0.5CoO3-δ cathode material for solid oxide fuel cell
